Our Methodology
	How We Find What Others Miss

	Our methodology mirrors how real attackers operate 
	methodical, patient, and relentless.

	1.Discovery

		We start by understanding your:
		  - Application architecture
		  - Tech stack
		  - Business logic
		  - High-value assets
		This allows us to focus on what actually matters.

	2.Reconnaissance

		We map the full attack surface by:
		 - Identifying entry points
		 - Enumerating roles and permissions
		 - Analyzing workflows and edge cases
		Just like a real attacker would.

